1
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:30,720
Hey there.

2
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:35,039
Is this your first time here?

3
00:01:35,039 --> 00:01:37,240
Want to check out some ancient costumes in our shop?

4
00:01:37,240 --> 00:01:38,300
Ancient costumes?

5
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:40,160
Have a bowl of tea first.

6
00:01:40,160 --> 00:01:41,160
It's refreshing.

7
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:43,600
Thank you.

8
00:01:49,160 --> 00:01:51,360
Snow lotus of the Queen Mother of the West,

9
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:52,890
ice spring from Mount Tian,

10
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:55,320
the medicine I brewed for 999 days!

11
00:01:55,320 --> 00:01:55,780
Well...

12
00:01:57,039 --> 00:01:57,640
I'm sorry.

13
00:01:58,640 --> 00:02:00,000
Luckily, it's a wooden bowl.

14
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:00,600
It's fine.

15
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:05,880
Men and women should keep their distance.

16
00:02:05,880 --> 00:02:06,960
I can do it myself.

17
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:09,080
I'm really sorry.

18
00:02:24,160 --> 00:02:25,040
Wear this.

19
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:33,890
Does this...

20
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:36,620
cost money?

21
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,240
It's free.

22
00:02:41,079 --> 00:02:41,800
Thank you.

23
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:43,800
Thanks.

24
00:02:45,760 --> 00:02:47,240
Give me the bag and the bowl.

25
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:47,720
Thanks.

26
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,020
The bag.

27
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:51,660
Thanks.

28
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:16,760
She looks exactly like

29
00:03:16,920 --> 00:03:18,780
the person I keep dreaming about.

30
00:03:18,880 --> 00:03:20,280
Is this a coincidence,

31
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:23,640
or is it really like what the old book vendor said

32
00:03:23,640 --> 00:03:24,700
about my past life?

33
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:36,680
Very handsome.

34
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:37,680
It suits you well.

35
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:40,720
Thank you.

36
00:03:41,160 --> 00:03:42,090
My name is Yuyao.

37
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:43,960
I'm the owner of this clothing store.

38
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:46,079
Portraits, travel photography, vlogs, I do it all.

39
00:03:46,079 --> 00:03:47,600
If you want to have fun,

40
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:48,760
I can be your guide

41
00:03:49,079 --> 00:03:51,410
and take you all around Tianshan Tianchi.

42
00:03:52,040 --> 00:03:52,760
After all,

43
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:54,560
since you're already here.

44
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:56,490
Why don't I add you on WeChat first?

45
00:03:58,079 --> 00:03:58,920
Yuyao.

46
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:01,120
Even the name is the same.

47
00:04:01,320 --> 00:04:02,580
Is this a coincidence?

48
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:04,240
Yuyao.

49
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:05,800
My name is Lu Sinian.

50
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:06,730
Nice to meet you.

51
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:11,060
I have something to do.

52
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,560
I'll leave first.

53
00:04:12,880 --> 00:04:15,280
I'll return the clothes to you another day.

54
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:17,089
The homestay is over there.

55
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:22,200
Why is it so difficult this time?

56
00:04:22,400 --> 00:04:24,530
He doesn't even want to say a word to me.

57
00:04:24,840 --> 00:04:26,300
It shouldn't be like this.

58
00:04:26,880 --> 00:04:29,000
How can I trigger his memories?

59
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:32,760
It seems everyone is here.

60
00:04:33,320 --> 00:04:34,050
The good show

61
00:04:34,840 --> 00:04:36,240
is about to begin.

62
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:40,580
I'm really looking forward to it.

63
00:04:57,159 --> 00:04:58,360
Lu Sinian.

64
00:04:58,840 --> 00:05:00,200
I don't have time

65
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:02,890
to wait for you to slowly recover your memory.

66
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:05,880
Old friend,

67
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:07,720
long time no see.

68
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:09,780
In every lifetime,

69
00:05:10,320 --> 00:05:11,650
you are still so stupid.

70
00:05:13,640 --> 00:05:15,760
Let me help you.

71
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,240
Yuyao.

72
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:07,040
Let's go, Sinian.

73
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:07,640
Let's go see

74
00:06:07,640 --> 00:06:09,570
how the fish we released are doing.

75
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:21,640
Yuyao.

76
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:26,660
What's wrong with you?

77
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:30,160
Yuyao.

78
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:32,680
Didn't you say you love him?

79
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:35,240
Why do you still want to kill him?

80
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:38,720
Of course I love him.

81
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:41,920
But he is a Heavenly Official.

82
00:06:42,400 --> 00:06:44,800
He could be dispatched and leave at any time.

83
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:46,440
As a deity of Yaochi,

84
00:06:47,159 --> 00:06:48,690
I have to stay here forever.

85
00:06:49,159 --> 00:06:50,240
It would be better

86
00:06:51,520 --> 00:06:53,280
to keep him here permanently

87
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:57,260
and let him become the best nourishment for all things.

88
00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:58,320
This way,

89
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:02,480
we can be together forever.

90
00:07:04,400 --> 00:07:07,530
It's impossible for you to keep him by your side forever.

91
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:10,050
I will keep waiting for his reincarnation

92
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:13,210
so he falls in love with me repeatedly.

93
00:07:13,840 --> 00:07:14,480
Then,

94
00:07:15,520 --> 00:07:18,560
he will willingly let me trap him here.

95
00:07:22,880 --> 00:07:25,560
You'd rather endure the suffering of reincarnation

96
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:27,680
than see how good I am to you?

97
00:07:57,400 --> 00:07:57,920
Yu...

98
00:07:58,200 --> 00:07:59,440
Yuyao.

99
00:08:01,080 --> 00:08:02,000
Yuyao.

100
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:08,680
Hi.

101
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:19,400
Your clothes,

102
00:08:19,400 --> 00:08:20,520
I washed them for you.

103
00:08:20,520 --> 00:08:21,160
Thanks.

104
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:26,480
Let's have breakfast together.

105
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,860
I don't eat breakfast.

106
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:30,080
I spent a long time making it.

107
00:08:30,280 --> 00:08:31,210
Please humor me.

108
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:34,850
Alright.

109
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,799
Then wait for me a sec.

110
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:37,320
Okay.

111
00:08:47,680 --> 00:08:49,840
Seeing so much good food right after waking up,

112
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:51,080
he must be so touched.

113
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:54,080
Memories need to be awakened bit by bit.

114
00:08:54,520 --> 00:08:56,380
I guess I owe you from my past life.

115
00:08:58,160 --> 00:08:59,720
Let me introduce them to you.

116
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:00,240
These

117
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:01,960
are Xinjiang specialties.

118
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,720
This is naan.

119
00:09:04,040 --> 00:09:05,600
This is a baked bun.

120
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:08,600
This is baursak.

121
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:10,460
It tastes better with jam.

122
00:09:10,920 --> 00:09:11,440
Try it.

123
00:09:14,800 --> 00:09:15,400
Thank you.

124
00:09:23,680 --> 00:09:24,810
There's a ring here.

125
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:55,360
Let's go, Sinian.

126
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:56,960
Lu Sinian.

127
00:09:58,680 --> 00:09:59,680
Don't resist it.

128
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:01,360
Open your heart.

129
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:05,050
This way you will know everything.

130
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:06,480
It seems

131
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:08,920
this is right.

132
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:10,120
What?

133
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:13,320
Did you remember something?

134
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:15,410
You remembered something, right?

135
00:10:17,160 --> 00:10:18,040
Who am I?

136
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:23,640
Boss Yuyao.

137
00:10:24,280 --> 00:10:25,000
I'm sorry.

138
00:10:25,560 --> 00:10:26,760
I want to go for a walk.

139
00:10:27,880 --> 00:10:28,680
You eat first.

140
00:10:35,400 --> 00:10:37,400
The Snow Lotus Ring is also useless.

141
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:39,320
This is the 99th time.

142
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:44,170
Is the Queen Mother of the West still intentionally separating us?

143
00:10:44,520 --> 00:10:45,280
Lu Sinian.

144
00:10:46,400 --> 00:10:48,200
Are we really going to fall short

145
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:49,520
at the very last step?

146
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:15,800
Everything is connected to this place.

147
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:16,850
Perhaps,

148
00:11:17,760 --> 00:11:18,600
only here

149
00:11:19,400 --> 00:11:21,000
can I find the answers I want.

150
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:25,200
Bo Peak reflects the snow's glow,

151
00:11:26,760 --> 00:11:29,360
Jade Pool ripples with slight blue.

152
00:11:30,400 --> 00:11:32,960
Lotus blooms with a thousand years of love,

153
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:34,360
boundless love,

154
00:11:34,760 --> 00:11:35,960
never to be broken.

155
00:11:40,480 --> 00:11:41,800
Boundless love,

156
00:11:42,520 --> 00:11:44,320
never to be broken.

157
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:48,000
You are that

158
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:51,360
old man who sold books.

159
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:53,360
Am I that ugly?

160
00:11:53,760 --> 00:11:54,720
Lu Sinian,

161
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:57,280
long time no see.
